snippet.title: Darkest Dungeon II - The Binding Blade DLC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
#darkestdungeon2 #bindingblade #redhook 

The Binding Blade DLC is available now on Steam and the Epic Games Store!

Steam: https://bit.ly/bindingbladesteam
Epic: https://bit.ly/bindingbladeepic

Get Darkest Dungeon II’s first DLC pack! This pack contains 2 new heroes with full playable backstories and a special unlock quest, a wandering mini-boss, and more.

Darkest Dungeon II on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1940340/Darkest_Dungeon_II/ 
Darkest Dungeon II on Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/darkest-dungeon-2 
Website: https://www.darkestdungeon.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/darkestdungeon
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DarkestDungeon
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DarkestDungeon
Instagram: https://instagram.com/redhookstudios
